title: Welcome to Luxury living!
posting_body: ['REF#: 11247003', 'Welcome to Luxury living !', 'Unbeatable Location near EVERYTHING IMAGINABLE!', 'Resort-style amenities clubhouse, pool, fitness center, dog park, tennis, and basketball court 24/7 guard gate.', 'large open floor plan, the kitchen has granite countertops, an island with a sink, and custom-made cabinets with brand-new stainless-steel appliances.', 'vaulted ceilings.', 'Large open balcony and porch, privately side patio sitting area to enjoy the beautiful south Florida weather.', 'tile floors in bathrooms and living areas, brand new carpet installed in bedrooms.', 'walking closet, roman tub and shower in the master bedroom, den/office on the second floor, freshly painted inside and out.', 'Hurricane Shutters, brand new solar panels generates major electricity for entire home.', 'VANESSA REID *|* REALTOR', 'COURTESY OF United Realty Group, Inc']
